rComments: Favourite 1st-year course! I found the class super engaging and think Michael is a great lecturer with a lot of knowledge in the field. HPS200 is a fairly easy course but the subject matter is really interesting if you're interested in philosophy but find some first/second-year PHL courses to be too meta (meaning not applicable to the real world).
